# Install these modules
pip install streamlit
pip install plotly
pip install scikit-learn
pip install scipy
pip install matplotlib
pip install tensorflow
pip install yfinance
pip install altair
pip install streamlit-authenticator
pip install yfinance --upgrade --no-cache-dir


# To run go to terminal and enter:
streamlit run main.py

This program is used for stock analysis. The main functionalities within this program are:

1) Stock prediction - using LSTM the program will predict stock prices given a stock ticker.
2) Stock returns - using a date range and ticker symbol the program will show what $1,000 invested in a given stock
would be at the end of the date range.
3) Volume analysis - using a date range and ticker symbol the program will show the volume for each day in the
date range.
4) Technical analysis - using a date range and ticker symbol the program will show the 60 day moving average vs.
the stock price over the given date range.